name: MAHILA UTTHAN
briefDescription: MAHILA UTTHAN, Village & Post Katrari, District - Deoria  is a Registered Society since 2001 and also registered with FCRA, 1976 and 12AA and 80G of Income Tax Act. Organization is Working in Deoria, Santkabir Nagar, Kushinagar District for the development of Art and culture in above districts of Uttar Pradesh . Main objective is given below :-1-	Cultural Programmers2-	Sanitation and hygine3-	Environment and tree plantation4-	Rural Development5-	Promote to Digital India6-	Skill Development & Women Empowerment
